<plot>Determined to follow in the footsteps of his late father, eleven-year-old Peter is obsessed with becoming a policeman and he's not willing to allow the fact he's just a little boy to stand in his way! Peter's usual cases involve petty crimes but things go awry when the boy and his fellow child partner Lisa find themselves on the trail of two thieves after the mayor's office is robbed. With his mother and the town chief determined to put an end to Peter's crimefighting, can he find the robbers before they make off with the loot?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?290885</url></doc>
